description: This repository is created for the course Data Preparation and Workflow Management taught at the university of Tilburg. Our goal is to compare a city's availability on Airbnb during a Formula 1 event with a city that is comparable, but where no event is hosted. As for the scientific method, we are going to implement a quasi-experiment.
